## 3.2.11 LLVM_BUILD_DIR
LLVM tar
```
122  wget http:/llvm.org/releases/9.0.0/llvm-9.0.0.src.tar.xz -O llvm-9.0.0.src.tar.xz
134  mkdir llvm_tarball
137  cp /mnt/hgfs/
138  cp /mnt/hgfs/vm_share/*.gz .
140  cp /mnt/hgfs/vm_share/*.xz . 
143  mv SPIRV-LLVM-Translator-9.0.0-1.tar.gz spv-9.0.0.tar.gz
145  md5sum *
```

